#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-235B-A22B.md:932
msgid "Q: What hardware is required for Qwen3-235B-A22B?"
msgstr "问：Qwen3-235B-A22B需要什么硬件？"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-235B-A22B.md:934
msgid ""
"For BF16: 1 Atlas 800I A3 (64G × 16) node, 1 Atlas 800I A2 (64G × 8) node, "
"or 2 Atlas 800I A2 (32G × 8) nodes. For W8A8 quantized version, the hardware"
" requirements are similar."
msgstr ""
"对于BF16：1个Atlas 800I A3 (64G × 16)节点，1个Atlas 800I A2 (64G × 8) 节点，或2个Atlas "
"800I A2 (32G × 8)节点。对于W8A8量化版本，硬件要求类似。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-235B-A22B.md:936
msgid "Q: How do I enable long context beyond 40K?"
msgstr "问：如何启用超过40K的长上下文？"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-235B-A22B.md:938
msgid ""
"Use yarn rope-scaling. For vLLM >= v0.12.0: `--hf-overrides "
"'{\"rope_parameters\": "
"{\"rope_type\":\"yarn\",\"rope_theta\":1000000,\"factor\":4,\"original_max_position_embeddings\":32768}}'`."
" For older versions, use `--rope_scaling`. Model variants like "
"Qwen3-235B-A22B-Instruct-2507 natively support long contexts and don't need "
"this parameter."
msgstr ""
"使用yarn rope-scaling。对于vLLM >= v0.12.0：`--hf-overrides '{\"rope_parameters\":"
" "
"{\"rope_type\":\"yarn\",\"rope_theta\":1000000,\"factor\":4,\"original_max_position_embeddings\":32768}}'`。对于旧版本，使用`--rope_scaling`。像Qwen3-235B-A22B-Instruct-2507这样的模型变体原生支持长上下文，无需此参数。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-235B-A22B.md:940
msgid "Q: When should I use PD disaggregation vs single-node deployment?"
msgstr "问：何时应使用PD分离部署而非单节点部署？"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-235B-A22B.md:942
msgid ""
"Single-node deployment is simpler and recommended when the model fits within"
" a single node. PD disaggregation separates Prefill and Decode across nodes,"
" enabling higher throughput for large-scale serving. For Qwen3-235B-A22B, "
"three A3 nodes with PD disaggregation can achieve ~3× the throughput of "
"single-node deployment."
msgstr ""
"单节点部署更简单，当模型适合单个节点时推荐使用。PD分离部署将Prefill和Decode分散到多个节点，可实现大规模服务的高吞吐量。对于Qwen3-235B-A22B，使用PD分离部署的三个A3节点可以达到单节点部署约3倍的吞吐量。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-235B-A22B.md:944
msgid "Q: What is the difference between `enable_fused_mc2=1` and `=2`?"
msgstr "问：`enable_fused_mc2=1` 和 `=2` 有什么区别？"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-235B-A22B.md:946
msgid ""
"Value `1` enables the base MoE fused operator, suitable for typical EP "
"configurations. Value `2` enables an alternative fusion strategy optimized "
"for large-scale EP (e.g., EP32 in PD disaggregation scenarios). Both are "
"experimental and currently only support W8A8 quantization on Atlas A3 "
"servers."
msgstr ""
"值`1`启用基础MoE融合算子，适用于典型的EP配置。值`2`启用针对大规模EP（例如PD分离场景中的EP32）优化的替代融合策略。两者均为实验性功能，目前仅在Atlas"
" A3服务器上支持W8A8量化。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-235B-A22B.md:948
msgid "Q: When should I use Expert Parallelism?"
msgstr "问：何时应使用专家并行？"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-235B-A22B.md:950
msgid ""
"Expert Parallelism (EP) should always be enabled for Qwen3-235B-A22B (an MoE"
" model) via `--enable-expert-parallel`. It distributes FFN experts across "
"NPUs to reduce per-device computation. EP works alongside TP, where MoE "
"layers use EP and non-MoE layers use TP."
msgstr ""
"对于Qwen3-235B-A22B（一个MoE模型），应始终通过`--enable-expert-"
"parallel`启用专家并行(EP)。它将FFN专家分布到多个NPU上以减少每设备计算量。EP与TP协同工作，其中MoE层使用EP，非MoE层使用TP。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-235B-A22B.md:952
msgid "Q: How do I choose between Context Parallelism and PD Disaggregation?"
msgstr "问：如何在上下文并行和PD分离部署之间选择？"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-235B-A22B.md:954
msgid ""
"Context Parallelism (CP) splits the KV cache of a single request across "
"multiple NPUs, suitable for long context scenarios on a single node. PD "
"Disaggregation separates Prefill and Decode across nodes, suitable for high-"
"throughput serving with many concurrent requests."
msgstr ""
"上下文并行(CP)将单个请求的KV缓存拆分到多个NPU上，适用于单节点上的长上下文场景。PD分离部署将Prefill和Decode分散到多个节点，适用于高并发请求的高吞吐量服务。"

